-Masuk.
-Sila masuk.

85
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:07,620
Tuan Muda, masuk dan duduk.

86
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:09,650
Datang lagi, Tuan muda.

87
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,380
Yang Mulia.

88
